data.description: Come on out to see this one of a kind immaculately maintained 4 bed, 2.5 bath traditional home. Near to coveted Ft. Bend ISD schools and Quail Valley. This won't last long!     With over 2200 square feet and a spacious 2 car garage, His/Hers master closets, this home has everything a family needs. Completely renovated in 2017 and kitchen done in 2021. Don't forget about the newly added covered patio in 2022. The fully fenced backyard will provide plenty of entertainment for years to come.    Nearby to HWY 90 and 6, also close to Fort Bend Parkway, you're sure to get anywhere you need in minutes.
